Text: Hi, I've never dl'd an app from TPB, usually just go through Installous but none of the DH links were working for me. Anyway, how do I put this on my iPod? Thanks!

use SSH and go to var/mobile/library/downloads 
put the app in there and go to installous and install it
Great upload!  Works like a charm on 3gs running iOS4.1.  Cool game if you're into games like Diablo.
